data.title: life Husband and Wife Duo
data.meta_description:
Catch up with real-life husband and wife duo Kassie and James DePaiva in The Locher Room. Kassie and James will be here to look back at their incredible careers and take us back to when they first met in Llaneview on One Life to Live.

The couple were married on May 31, 1996 and will celebrate their 28th anniversary this year. James joined the cast of One Life to Live as Max Holden in 1987 and Kassie moved over to Llaneview as Blair Cramer in 1993 where she remained until the show went off the air. It was 30 years ago last December 17th that Blair made her debut.

Sit down, grab a cup of joe and catch up with Kassie & James right here in The Locher Room.
